=pod

=head1 INVENTORY - CURRENT ROADMAP

=head2
1.1 IMMEDIATE REQUIREMENTS

=over 4

=item [feature] add a change audit trail

=item [feature] add optional date field which holds the end-of-life date of
   the hardware model
  
=item [feature] Add a service level to support contracts.
 
=item [feature] Show all devices under a support contract / show all not under a
   support contract.
 
=item [feature] Support contracts: cost and duration of contract, start and end
   date plus service level.
   
=item [feature] ability to see all devices which are of a particular model type
 
=item [defect] From the server side show a sane explanitor error message if
the intended hostname already exists.
   
=item [defect] On the quickdevice page, show a more accurate helpful error
message if the hostname of a ups device being created already exists.
 
=item [release] Write tests for each module
 
=item [release] Improve install instructions

=item [release] Put license details in each file


=back

=head2
1.2 LONGER TERM ISSUES

=over 4

=item [defect] on the quick device addition page the submit button is
accidentally enabled when only one essential field is filled in

=item [defect] new update system gives a blank page if 'manifest' setting is
   missing from ini file

=item [defect] new update system has no reset/recheck system

=item [defect] On the photos page make it use a sha hash as the complete filename

=item [defect] dont let a ups be its own ups

=item [defect] IPv6 name resolution, e.g. add a IPv6 interface that rsolves to a host and the inventory will read ' unresolved'

=item [feature] script to check/update cached dns records overnight

=item [feature] Introduce edit restrictions on the groups (frodos/ups and status)
      where names mustn't change

=item [feature] JQuery - Show a date picker widget on date fields

=item [feature] Ajax - As the user types, show if the name is unique and
      available or not (tick or cross)

=item [feature] Make problem search run each night as a scheduled job

=item [release] Improve test coverage

=back

=head2
1.3 ADD FUNCTIONALITY

=over 4

=item [feature] "show a host whose details haven't been checked in the last year"
 
=item [feature] "show me a random problem and hint how I might fix it"
 
=item [feature] add ability to view the change log from the web interface
 
=item [feature] add geolocation data for locations

=item [release] improve test coverage

=item [release] add a manual

=back

=head2
1.4 CONTROLLED UPDATE SYSTEM

=over 4

=item [release] Update system needs lots of work

=over 4

=item Package integrity check (manifest plus sha256) versus files in that
      release
     
=item Ability to have local menu items
     
=item Ability to have local scripts
     
=item one button update check
     
=item ajax style async update
     
=item browsed pages are made not to break when updated (apache distress)

=back

=back

